The frozen `outputs/` directories contain text generated by third-party large
language models. Those outputs are NOT covered by the MIT license above and
remain subject to the respective model providers' terms:

  * Qwen2.5-Coder (3B, 7B)        — Apache License 2.0
  * LongCat-2.0                    — MIT License
  * DeepSeek-V4-Flash              — MIT License
